<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h1>
    <p>
      You've received this e-mail because Project Coordinator <%= @project_coordinator.name %> needs help with <strong><%= @event.name %></strong>. 
      We thought you'd be a great match for this volunteer event based on the following skill(s):
      <ul>
      <% @event.matching_skills(@user).each do |skill| %>
      <li><%= skill %></li>
      <% end %> 
      </ul>




      If you're free on <strong><%= @event.formatted_start %></strong> please consider helping out. <br>
    </p>
    <p><%= link_to('Click here to sign-up', event_url(@event.id), method: :patch) %>!</p>
    <p>Note: You may have to sign in to your Volunteerly account to join an event first!</p>
  </body>
</html>